Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.63,0:17:00.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.26,0:17:02.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝福者！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.35,0:17:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你找到了我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.84,0:17:13.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是有趣的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.44,0:17:14.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.17,0:17:33.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里奈前辈 请脱离！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.86,0:17:44.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利用同步来同化驾驶员吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.52,0:17:52.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同化促进剂 1号到3号 给药
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.52,0:18:09.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同步状态 强制解除
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.92,0:18:17.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里奈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.97,0:18:18.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彗…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:21.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们隔绝了我的祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.49,0:18:24.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你还和我在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.35,0:18:37.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 停下 停下！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.71,0:18:45.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 大家快躲开…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.28,0:18:48.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芬里尔 认证代码确认
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.04,0:18:59.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}9 8 7 6 5 4 3 2 1
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.76,0:18:51.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.37,0:18:53.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里奈前辈 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.85,0:18:55.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里奈前辈！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.70,0:18:57.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 晖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.62,0:19:00.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.10,0:19:23.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然想消除自己？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.35,0:19:27.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接招吧 祝福者！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.36,0:19:29.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.03,0:19:50.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 被他们争取到时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.45,0:19:53.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再不快点总士他们就要被带走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.78,0:20:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你快去 美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.67,0:20:22.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算能起飞了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.65,0:20:23.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是多亏了你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.47,0:20:26.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很感谢你 马里斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.51,0:20:29.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是多亏了你才能离开那个岛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.32,0:20:32.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实你很恨我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.01,0:20:36.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对你将创造的世界是寄予期待的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.13,0:20:38.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普罗米修斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.10,0:20:41.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是人类给我起的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.60,0:20:42.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.67,0:20:44.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们叫我尊者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.50,0:20:46.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「海神的尊者」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.68,0:20:48.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后我该怎么叫你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.18,0:20:50.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛列斯佩罗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.77,0:20:54.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我给人类的最后一句话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.94,0:20:56.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道是什么意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.77,0:20:58.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「绝望」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.77,0:20:58.62,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,注：世界语中「绝望」发音为「玛列斯佩罗」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.42,0:21:01.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很值得期待吧 马里斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.06,0:21:17.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别走！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.24,0:21:18.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马里斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.44,0:21:38.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了 回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.83,0:21:41.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别逼我开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.79,0:21:44.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你下不了手的 美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.50,0:21:49.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是预测了未来 才带上我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.22,0:23:04.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总士…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.12,0:23:21.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机体被抢走了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.95,0:23:22.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.19,0:23:24.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑不会不见的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.50,0:23:27.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他的心会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.10,0:23:31.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他会不再觉得天空美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.76,0:23:35.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在往后的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.36,0:23:38.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样或许更好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.69,0:24:08.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普罗米修斯Mir在大气层外形成了极大的领域
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.52,0:24:12.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和海神岛的内核…所预言的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.16,0:24:14.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行动失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.91,0:24:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,探讨一下该如何挽回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.07,0:24:22.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则 世界和我们的故乡都会毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.77,0:24:59.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能感觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.31,0:25:04.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常大的力量升上了天空
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.17,0:25:06.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要做好准备
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.93,0:25:11.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使我们的未来在今后的未来中不被毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.80,0:25:15.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 露维·卡玛大人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.76,0:25:19.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望并没有消失
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.06,0:25:21.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要悲伤 美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.43,0:25:31.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.40,0:25:35.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.23,0:25:47.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在和平的地方生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.47,0:25:51.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抛弃那个
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.80,0:25:54.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牺牲一些人来让另一些人活下去的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.43,0:25:56.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总士
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.87,0:26:06.04,Default,NTP,0,0,80,,{\fnMingLiU\fs60\shad2\bord0\fad(800,800)\4c&H000000&}—— 三 年 后 ——
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.80,0:26:35.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.10,0:26:39.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对面有些什么呢
